<lb n="0401a13"/><p>淨念珠真言合掌捧珠</p>
<lb n="0401a14"/><p type="dharani">唵阿娜步<note place="inline">二合</note>帝尾惹曳悉地悉馱羅梯<note place="inline">二合</note><term lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;
